txt.en: Precious timber awaits those who brave the hidden dangers of the ethereal crevasse of Clovengap.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Clovengap: Terror in the Trees to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>

The scout gives you a missive to collect logs.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Clovengap: Terror in the Trees to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
